{"tid":2256483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懶理醜聞續撐拜登 勒邦占士暗諷trump係小丑","createTime":"2020-10-24T11:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T11:44:44.000Z","uid":75656,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6718459f193573d904bba6a5759ddd6fafc296","tid":2256483,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"特朗普與拜登在香港時間周五早上，進行了大選前最後一場電視辯論。在民調中落後的特朗普猛烈攻擊拜登，特別對亨特的「電郵門」醜聞窮追猛打，質疑拜登擔任前總統奧巴馬副手期間，讓兒子在烏克蘭及中國做生意時，利用他的身份牟利。不過，早已表明會為拜登助選的勒邦占士，顯然未被事件影響，他在Instagram貼出了一張特朗普與拜登辯論的電視截圖，並以小丑emoji遮蓋着特朗普的頭部，暗諷他是一個小丑，同時呼籲選民投票。<br />\n<br />\nLBJ在16年大選曾在俄亥俄州為民主候選人希拉莉站台，而他早前接受傳媒訪問時已表明，會在今屆選舉為拜登及賀錦麗助選。LBJ因為不滿國內黑人民權狀況，表明反對特朗普連任，<span class=\"red\">由他牽頭的倡議組織「More Than A Vote」，亦正跟美國前總統奧巴馬的妻子米歇爾合作，與對方旗下的組織「When We All Vote」，攜手呼籲選民參與投票。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201023/KM27SE7IX5C35O6MLKUJD3JT6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201023%2FKM27SE7IX5C35O6MLKUJD3JT6E%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=4f75844a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201023%2FKM27SE7IX5C35O6MLKUJD3JT6E%2F&h=94053e3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201023/KM27SE7IX5C35O6MLKUJD3JT6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wNbhFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wNbhFS.jpg&h=20752e50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdc6778ed64a3c722806fa1b6ac14c5e7dc4e6cb","tid":2256483,"uid":28432,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"佢講唔講得出拜登幫黑人做過啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6abbfbb062908890d8dc87e3ae036c31085fe83","tid":2256483,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a3ab3525194cf4447b